%e A396497 2 is a term since (90*k-1, 120*k-1, 180*k-1, 240*k-1, 360*k-1, 720*k-1) = (179, 239, 359, 479, 719, 1439) are all primes. This corresponds to the 4 consecutive members (1436, 1437, 1438, 1439) in A395563.
%e A396497 14973 is a term since (1347569, 1796759, 2695139, 3593519, 5390279, 10780559) are all primes. This corresponds to the 4 consecutive members (10780556, 10780557, 10780558, 10780559) in A395563.
%o A396497 (PARI) isA396497(k) = isprime(90*k-1) && isprime(120*k-1) && isprime(180*k-1) && isprime(240*k-1) && isprime(360*k-1) && isprime(720*k-1)
